{"id":1276,"date":"2024-08-04T18:15:24","date_gmt":"2024-08-04T18:15:24","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1276"},"modified":"2024-12-31T21:16:40","modified_gmt":"2024-12-31T21:16:40","slug":"mission-076","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-076\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #076: Tomb Raider"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">Mission #076: Tomb Raider<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Great Desert, Tomb of Borrius 1F &#8211; Ruin Maniac at slide puzzle<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Become Pok\u00e9mon Champion<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Explore the Tomb of Borrius<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td><u>Item<\/u>: <strong>Psychium Z<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>An archaeologist is trying to get into the Tomb of Borrius. Take him to the treasure chamber and he\u2019ll give you a Psychium Z.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to Dehara City and head east out of the gate. You\u2019ll end up in the Great Desert.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/01-pokemon-unbound-dehara-city-east-gate.jpg\" alt=\"Dehara City east gate \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Dehara City east gate<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>From there, hug the cliff wall to the south and walk east until you find two canyon entrances to the south, each with a cactus in front of them.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/02-pokemon-unbound-the-cacti-and-the-canyons.jpg\" alt=\"The cacti and the canyons \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The cacti and the canyons<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Take the canyon entrance behind the smaller cactus &#8211; the other one is blocked.<\/p>\n<p>Head south until you reach an open area, and then hug the north wall walking east.<\/p>\n<p>You\u2019ll see the entrance to the Tomb of Borrius immediately, on the east side of that little valley.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/03-pokemon-unbound-the-tomb-of-borrius.jpg\" alt=\"The Tomb of Borrius \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Tomb of Borrius<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Head inside to the entrance chamber and you\u2019ll see a Ruin Maniac in front of a puzzle.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/04-pokemon-unbound-the-entrance-chamber.jpg\" alt=\"The entrance chamber \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The entrance chamber<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>If you\u2019re Pok\u00e9mon Champion, he steps aside to let you solve it.<\/p>\n<p>It\u2019s a tile puzzle depicting a Ho-Oh, and you\u2019ll need to rearrange the tiles to their intended positions to continue. Below is the completed puzzle solution:<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/05-pokemon-unbound-the-completed-puzzle-image.jpg\" alt=\"The completed puzzle image \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The completed puzzle image<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you do this, a hole opens up beneath you and you drop multiple floors before landing in B4F.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/06-pokemon-unbound-the-mission-is-to-explore.jpg\" alt=\"The mission is to explore \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The mission is to explore<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Ruin Maniac throws down a ladder so you\u2019re not trapped down there, and comes down himself to investigate.<\/p>\n<p>Your mission is to find the burial chamber and then escape with any treasure you may find.<\/p>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<h3>B4F \u2013 Dusknoir Boulder Puzzle<\/h3>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/07-pokemon-unbound-b4f-is-a-boulder-puzzle-floor.jpg\" alt=\"B4F is a boulder puzzle floor \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>B4F is a boulder puzzle floor<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The first obstacle you\u2019ll need to clear is a boulder puzzle, with a slight twist. There are multiple Dusknoir on this floor whose line of sight needs to be blocked.<\/p>\n<p>If they see you, you\u2019ll be sent back to the ladder.<\/p>\n<p>The quickest way to solve the puzzle is as follows:<\/p>\n<p><strong>Step 1:<\/strong> Break the southernmost rock with Rock Smash.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/08-pokemon-unbound-before-the-1st-move.jpg\" alt=\"Before the first move \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Before the first move<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Step 2:<\/strong> Push the southernmost boulder east to the wall.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/09-pokemon-unbound-after-the-1st-move.jpg\" alt=\"After the first move \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>After the first move<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Step 3:<\/strong> Push the boulder all the way north along the eastern wall until it hits a rock you can smash.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/10-pokemon-unbound-after-the-3rd-move.jpg\" alt=\"After the third move \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>After the third move<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Step 4:<\/strong> Smash the bottom rock with Rock Smash.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/11-pokemon-unbound-after-the-4th-move.jpg\" alt=\"After the fourth move \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>After the fourth move<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Step 5:<\/strong> Push the boulder north one space. Then push it all the way east to the button. This will disable the wall of fire.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/12-pokemon-unbound-after-the-5th-move.jpg\" alt=\"After the fifth move \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>After the fifth move<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Step 6:<\/strong> Walk down to the remaining boulder.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/13-pokemon-unbound-the-remaining-boulder.jpg\" alt=\"The remaining boulder \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The remaining boulder<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Step 7:<\/strong> Push this boulder east to the eastern wall, and then push it south until it is one tile away from the southern wall (not touching the wall).<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/14-pokemon-unbound-after-the-7th-move.jpg\" alt=\"After the seventh move \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>After the seventh move<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Step 8:<\/strong> Push the boulder all the way east until it blocks the vision of the Dusknoir.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/15-pokemon-unbound-after-the-8th-move.jpg\" alt=\"After the eighth move \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>After the eighth move<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Step 9:<\/strong> Walk east and follow the passage up until you see two boulders and a rock blocking the way forward.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/16-pokemon-unbound-after-the-9th-move.jpg\" alt=\"After the ninth move \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>After the ninth move<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Step 10:<\/strong> Push the leftmost boulder north until it is directly east of the next button.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/17-pokemon-unbound-after-the-10th-move.jpg\" alt=\"After the tenth move \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>After the tenth move<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Step 11:<\/strong> Push the boulder west onto the button. This will make the Dusknoir ahead turn to face the wall.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/18-pokemon-unbound-after-the-eleventh-move.jpg\" alt=\"After the eleventh move \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>After the eleventh move<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Step 12:<\/strong> Walk back down to the southern side of the boulder that\u2019s next to the smashable rock.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/19-pokemon-unbound-after-the-twelfth-move.jpg\" alt=\"After the twelfth move \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>After the twelfth move<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Step 13:<\/strong> Push the boulder north one space.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/20-pokemon-unbound-after-the-thirteenth-move.jpg\" alt=\"After the thirteenth move \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>After the thirteenth move<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Step 14:<\/strong> Push the boulder west to the wall.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/21-pokemon-unbound-after-the-fourteenth-move.jpg\" alt=\"After the fourteenth move \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>After the fourteenth move<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Step 15:<\/strong> Push the boulder north twice so it is on the same horizontal line as the boulder on the button.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/22-pokemon-unbound-after-the-fifteenth-move.jpg\" alt=\"After the fifteenth move \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>After the fifteenth move<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><strong>Step 16:<\/strong> Push the boulder all the way north so it blocks the vision of the final Dusknoir next to the ladder.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/23-pokemon-unbound-after-the-final-move.jpg\" alt=\"After the final move \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>After the final move<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>With that, you\u2019re free to proceed around the Dusknoir and get to the ladder.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/24-pokemon-unbound-the-way-to-the-ladder-is-clear.jpg\" alt=\"The way to the ladder is clear \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The way to the ladder is clear<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Climb it and you\u2019ll end up on B3F.<\/p>\n<h3>B3F &#8211; Lava Stepping Stone Puzzle<\/h3>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/25-pokemon-unbound-an-unexpected-volcano.jpg\" alt=\"An unexpected volcano \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>An unexpected volcano<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll end up on a floor almost completely covered in lava. To get around, you\u2019ll need to navigate on a series of stepping stones.<\/p>\n<p>From the ladder platform, go south until you step on the first stepping stone.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/26-pokemon-unbound-the-1st-stepping-stone.jpg\" alt=\"The first stepping stone \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The first stepping stone<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Then, follow them east.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/27-pokemon-unbound-the-1st-junction.jpg\" alt=\"The first junction \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The first junction<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll get to a junction of stones almost immediately. Jump onto the southern path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/28-pokemon-unbound-the-2nd-junction.jpg\" alt=\"The second junction \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The second junction<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>From there, go down and then take the path that starts from the western stone.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/29-pokemon-unbound-moving-along-the-path.jpg\" alt=\"Moving along the path \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Moving along the path<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>This path of stepping stones will snake around until it eventually starts heading northeast.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/30-pokemon-unbound-the-3rd-junction.jpg\" alt=\"The third junction \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The third junction<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll reach a junction that looks like a square &#8211; head for the path leading from the northeast stone.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/31-pokemon-unbound-the-northeast-stone-of-the-junction.jpg\" alt=\"The northeast stone of the junction \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The northeast stone of the junction<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>From there, follow it generally north as it snakes around the lava.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/32-pokemon-unbound-another-snaky-path.jpg\" alt=\"Another snaky path \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Another snaky path<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll eventually pass a junction whose western path leads to an item &#8211; continue on past it and the stones will lead east.<\/p>\n<p>Continue until you see another junction (pictured below). Take the northern path here to an island.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/33-pokemon-unbound-the-4th-junction.jpg\" alt=\"The fourth junction \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The fourth junction<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>There\u2019s a rock on the island that acts as a switch when activated.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/34-pokemon-unbound-the-1st-rock-switch.jpg\" alt=\"The first rock switch \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The first rock switch<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you activate the switch, there will be a rumbling, and some paths will have shifted.<\/p>\n<p>Go back to the junction you were just at, and this time head east.<\/p>\n<p>There will soon be another junction &#8211; take the southern path and you\u2019ll see that the path leads to an island with an item on it. Follow it through.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/35-pokemon-unbound-head-south-from-the-next-junction.jpg\" alt=\"Head south from the next junction \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Head south from the next junction<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/36-pokemon-unbound-on-the-other-side-of-the-island.jpg\" alt=\"On the other side of the island \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>On the other side of the island<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Pass over that island until you get to a four-way junction of stones. Take the eastern path here until you get to another island with a rock on it.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/37-pokemon-unbound-the-2nd-rock-switch.jpg\" alt=\"The second rock switch \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The second rock switch<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Activate the second rock and the paths will shift again &#8211; a new path will appear to the north.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/38-pokemon-unbound-jump-onto-the-new-path.jpg\" alt=\"Jump onto the new path \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Jump onto the new path<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Take the new path west until you get to the same island that had an item on it.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/39-pokemon-unbound-the-paths-have-changed.jpg\" alt=\"The paths have changed \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The paths have changed<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The paths leading from this island have now changed \u2013 you want to take the southern path here and follow it along.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/40-pokemon-unbound-following-the-stones.jpg\" alt=\"Following the stones \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the stones<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Keep going south and west until you reach an island with a rock on it.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/41-pokemon-unbound-the-switchless-rock.jpg\" alt=\"The switchless rock \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The switchless rock<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>This rock doesn\u2019t have a switch, though. Ignore it and take the southwest path.<\/p>\n<p>Follow the stones west, past the junction, and the path will turn south.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/42-pokemon-unbound-going-south.jpg\" alt=\"Going south \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Going south<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Keep following them until you get to another junction of stones.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/43-pokemon-unbound-take-the-path-to-the-island.jpg\" alt=\"Take the path to the island \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Take the path to the island<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go south from this junction and land on the island with the item on it.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/44-pokemon-unbound-go-left-from-that-island-and-youll-see-another-rock-switch.jpg\" alt=\"Go left from that island and you\u2019ll see another rock switch \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Go left from that island and you\u2019ll see another rock switch<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Then take the west path and you\u2019ll find yourself near another rock switch.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/45-pokemon-unbound-the-3rd-rock-switch.jpg\" alt=\"The third rock switch \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The third rock switch<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Touch this rock switch to change the paths again.<\/p>\n<p>Then take the new south path to follow it south and east.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/46-pokemon-unbound-the-south-path.jpg\" alt=\"The south path \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The south path<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/47-pokemon-unbound-pass-the-next-junction.jpg\" alt=\"Pass the next junction \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Pass the next junction<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Keep going along the southern wall, passing the chance to go north to an island. Keep going northeast.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/48-pokemon-unbound-follow-it-to-a-small-island.jpg\" alt=\"Follow it to a small island \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Follow it to a small island<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>This path leads to a small island &#8211; cross it and continue north along the stones.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/49-pokemon-unbound-returning-to-the-1st-switch.jpg\" alt=\"Returning to the first switch \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Returning to the first switch<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll get to the first rock switch again. Activate it one more time, then head exactly back the way you came until you get to the small island.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/50-pokemon-unbound-the-small-islands-paths-have-changed.jpg\" alt=\"The small island\u2019s paths have changed \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The small island\u2019s paths have changed<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>From the small island, take the path leading east.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/51-pokemon-unbound-the-ladder-out-of-the-lava.jpg\" alt=\"The ladder out of the lava \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The ladder out of the lava<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll finally make it to the ladder to the next floor, and you can leave all that lava behind.<\/p>\n<h3>B2F &#8211; Dusknoir Haze Puzzle<\/h3>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/52-pokemon-unbound-this-floor-can-be-hard-to-navigate.jpg\" alt=\"This floor can be hard to navigate \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>This floor can be hard to navigate<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you get to B2F, you\u2019ll notice that your vision gets more and more blurry with each step.<\/p>\n<p>Here\u2019s how to complete this puzzle:<\/p>\n<p>From the ladder, head north.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> There are Dusknoir on this floor who will teleport you back to the ladder if they see you. They\u2019re stationary, but they shift around. They will also immediately spot you if you\u2019re running, so if you have always running enabled, hold the B button so you move at a walking pace.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/53-pokemon-unbound-the-t-junction.jpg\" alt=\"The T-junction \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The T-junction<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll get to a T-junction. Take the west path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/54-pokemon-unbound-slip-behind-this-dusknoir.jpg\" alt=\"Slip behind this Dusknoir \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Slip behind this Dusknoir<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Take the first northern path at the first opportunity so you can get behind the Dusknoir and follow that way west.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/55-pokemon-unbound-keep-going-west.jpg\" alt=\"Keep going west \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Keep going west<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Keep on going west until you can\u2019t go any further. <\/p>\n<p>It will become even harder and harder to see, so you\u2019ll need to make your way by \u201cfeeling\u201d for the walls by bumping them.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/56-pokemon-unbound-turn-south.jpg\" alt=\"Turn south \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Turn south<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you can\u2019t go west any further, turn south and follow the path of least resistance.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/57-pokemon-unbound-then-go-east.jpg\" alt=\"Then go east \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Then go east<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll hit another wall, which is your cue to start moving east.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/58-pokemon-unbound-keep-going.jpg\" alt=\"Keep going \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Keep going<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Again, keep going until you can\u2019t go further in that direction, being mindful of Dusknoir.<\/p>\n<p>Head south when you can, making sure not to run.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/59-pokemon-unbound-the-final-stretch.jpg\" alt=\"The final stretch \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The final stretch<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll reach a point where you can head west again \u2013 here you\u2019ll want to head to the southwest corner of the room.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/60-pokemon-unbound-nearly-there.jpg\" alt=\"Nearly there \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Nearly there<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>From the western wall, follow the path north.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/61-pokemon-unbound-the-ladder.jpg\" alt=\"The ladder \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The ladder<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The blurry object in the northwest corner of the room is your way off this floor &#038; it\u2019s the completion of this puzzle.<\/p>\n<h3>B1F &#8211; Cracked Floor Puzzle<\/h3>\n<p>You\u2019ll arrive on B1F, and encounter probably one of the most difficult and frustrating puzzles in the game.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/62-pokemon-unbound-cracked-floors.jpg\" alt=\"Cracked floors \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Cracked floors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The floor all around here is cracked, and if you linger too long on a cracked floor, you\u2019ll be sent to the ladder on the floor below.<\/p>\n<p>However, running isn\u2019t fast enough. Not even riding on the Motorcycle is fast enough &#8211; except if you use turbo mode, which you can by holding B. You\u2019ll need to ride your Motorcycle holding B across <strong>all of the gaps<\/strong>, and one wrong move will send you back to the very beginning of the puzzle.<\/p>\n<div class=\"callout-box\">\n<strong>Tip:<\/strong> If you\u2019re using an emulator, there\u2019s a way to cheese this puzzle.  Slow the emulator down to at least 20% of normal speed, so you can control when you can stop and when you have to turn easier.\n<\/div>\n<p>From the left-hand tile, race south onto a patch of solid ground. Then, continue east until you hit a 2&#215;2 square.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/63-pokemon-unbound-the-1st-gap.jpg\" alt=\"The first gap \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The first gap<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/64-pokemon-unbound-the-2x2-square.jpg\" alt=\"The 2x2 square \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The 2&#215;2 square<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>From the top right tile of that square, head south across the cracks.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/65-pokemon-unbound-the-platform-to-the-south.jpg\" alt=\"The platform to the south \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The platform to the south<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Then turn east and race along another patch until you hit a pillar.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/66-pokemon-unbound-the-pillar.jpg\" alt=\"The pillar \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The pillar<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>From the pillar, race across the cracks to the north.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/67-pokemon-unbound-near-the-north-wall.jpg\" alt=\"Near the north wall \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Near the north wall<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Then race east until you see a platform near a ladder.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/68-pokemon-unbound-keep-going-until-you-hit-the-ladder.jpg\" alt=\"Keep going until you hit the ladder \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Keep going until you hit the ladder<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Charge on through, and eventually you\u2019ll make it to the northeast corner of the floor and to the final ladder in the tomb.<\/p>\n<h3>Burial Chamber<\/h3>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/69-pokemon-unbound-the-burial-chamber.jpg\" alt=\"The burial chamber \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The burial chamber<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll finally arrive in the burial chamber of the Tomb of Borrius, and there\u2019s a lot of treasure for you to pick up.<\/p>\n<p>Take all the Relic items on the long tables before attempting to reach the item on the large coffin. This will activate the security system!<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/70-pokemon-unbound-leave-the-large-coffin-until-last.jpg\" alt=\"Leave the large coffin until last \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Leave the large coffin until last<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>It\u2019s a <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/pokemon\/magearna\/\">Magearna<\/a>, and the only one in the game. It will inflate to Dynamax size, so you\u2019ll need to defeat it with two Pok\u00e9mon.<\/p>\n<p>After defeating it, you\u2019ll get the option to capture it.<\/p>\n<table class=\"table grey center\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"class=\"text-large center\">Dynamax Battle<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Dynamax<br \/>\n          Magearna<\/strong><br \/>\n          Steel\/Fairy<br \/>\n          (Lv.50)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/71-pokemon-unbound-dynamax-magearna.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:300px;\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/076\/72-pokemon-unbound-your-reward.jpg\" alt=\"Your reward \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Your reward<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>For braving the dangers of the Tomb of Borrius, you\u2019ll get the <strong>Psychium Z<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<p>In addition, all those Relic items you may have picked up in the tomb will sell for a hefty price at Gurun Town.<\/p>\n<p>Once you complete this mission, Mission #079: Treasure Hunter becomes available.<\/p>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1277,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1276","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1276","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1277"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1276"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1276"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}